        "id": "Akhirnya kita bertemu.",
        "ar": "أخيرًا التقينا."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "6867fb313e9f070e832556a0",
      "index": 3,
      "text": "Now, as planned, I'll destroy you and, of course, that reporter you always do interviews with.",
      "startMs": 21975,
      "endMs": 36710,
      "ipa": "naʊ, æz plænd, aɪl dɪˈstrɔɪ juː ænd, ɒv kɔːs, ðæt rɪˈpɔːtə juː ˈɔːlweɪz duː ˈɪntəvjuːz wɪð",
      "translations": {
        "vi": "Bây giờ, theo kế hoạch, tôi sẽ tiêu diệt bạn và tất nhiên, phóng viên mà bạn luôn phỏng vấn",
        "th": "ตอนนี้ ตามแผน ฉันจะกำจัดนายและแน่นอน รวมถึงนักข่าวที่นายให้สัมภาษณ์ด้วย",
        "id": "Sekarang, sesuai rencana, aku akan menghancurkanmu dan, tentu saja, reporter yang selalu kau wawancarai itu.",
        "ar": "الآن، كما هو مُخطط، سأُدمركَ، وبالطبع ذلكَ الصحفي الذي تُجري معه دائمًا المُقابلات."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "6867fb313e9f070e832556a2",
      "index": 4,
      "text": "Who raised you as a child?",
      "startMs": 36760,
      "endMs": 40004,
      "ipa": "huː reɪzd juː æz ə ʧaɪld",
      "translations": {
        "vi": "Ai nuôi nấng con khi còn nhỏ",
        "th": "ใครเลี้ยงดูนายมาตั้งแต่เด็ก?",
        "id": "Siapa yang membesarkanmu saat kecil?",
        "ar": "مَن رَبَّاكَ وأنتَ طفل؟"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "6867fb313e9f070e832556a4",
      "index": 5,
      "text": "I'll kill them too.",
      "startMs": 40054,
      "endMs": 42334,
      "ipa": "aɪl kɪl ðɛm tuː",
      "translations": {
        "vi": "Tôi cũng sẽ giết chúng",
        "th": "ฉันจะฆ่าพวกมันด้วย",
        "id": "Aku juga akan membunuh mereka.",
        "ar": "سأقتلهم أيضًا."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "6867fb313e9f070e832556a6",
      "index": 6,
      "text": "No matter what you do to me, Luthor, your plans won't work.",
      "startMs": 42384,
      "endMs": 66911,
      "ipa": "nəʊ ˈmætə wɒt juː duː tuː miː, Luthor, jɔː plænz wəʊnt wɜːk",
      "translations": {
        "vi": "Dù anh có làm gì với tôi, Luthor, kế hoạch của anh cũng không thành công",
        "th": "ไม่ว่านายจะทำอะไรกับฉัน ลูเธอร์ แผนของนายก็ไม่มีทางสำเร็จ",
        "id": "Apa pun yang kau lakukan padaku, Luthor, rencanamu tak akan berhasil.",
        "ar": "مهما فعلتَ بي يا لوثر، لن تنجح خططك."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "6867fb313e9f070e832556a8",
      "index": 7,
      "text": "Wrap it up.",
      "startMs": 66961,
      "endMs": 70513,
      "ipa": "ræp ɪt ʌp",
      "translations": {
        "vi": "Quấn nó lại",
        "th": "ม้วนมันซะ",
        "id": "Bungkuslah.",
        "ar": "لفّه."
